1. *Uma* je čudo. (The mind is a wonder.)
2. *Um* je sposoban da se poveže sa mnogo informacija. (The mind is capable of connecting to many information.)
3. On je imao ogroman *um*. (He had a great mind.)
4. Ona je u stanju da razume *umove* drugih. (She is able to understand the minds of others.)
5. On je uspeo da razume *umove* drugih ljudi. (He succeeded in understanding the minds of other people.)